NightViper lay quite in the chamber... He smiled and somewhere deep inside 
his mind he thought of Starstorm... she'd protected him, and inside himself 
he remembered something... a place... peace... a land of bio-mechanical 
forrests and it all seemed peaceful and he was there but different... He 
awoke surprised... he was in some sort of chamber... a stasis pod... NO! he 
didn't want to go into a stasis pod... it took it all away... he didn't want 
to lose who he was... He changed and began clawing at the walls frantically.

--part1_16e.1df688fb.2be3543d_boundary
